关于锡吕‧玛塔吉女士的预言

1982年1月31日

讲于绍拉布尔(Sholapur)

Shri Mataji: Khandhavara, [Unclear].
Sahaja-Yogini: You choke it a little bit. [It seems that they are cooking]
